<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 text-black dark:text-white p-3 md:p-6 transition-colors duration-300"
     data-controller="exercise-checker text-toggle font-controls"
     data-text-toggle-target="content"
     data-font-controls-target="content">

  <%= render 'shared/page_header', pagina: @pagina %>

  <!-- Esercizio 1: Scrivi le frasi al condizionale -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl border-4 border-yellow-200 dark:border-yellow-700 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6" data-controller="fill-blanks">
    <h2 class="font-bold text-yellow-700 dark:text-yellow-400 mb-3">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="bg-yellow-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">1</span>
          <span class="bg-yellow-400 text-blue-800 px-2 py-1 rounded font-bold whitespace-nowrap">IMPARARE TUTTI</span>
        </div>
        <span>Scrivi le frasi utilizzando i verbi al <span class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 font-bold underline">condizionale</span> per rendere le domande più cortesi. Osserva l'esempio.</span>
      </div>
    </h2>

    <div class="bg-yellow-50 dark:bg-yellow-900/30 border-2 border-yellow-200 dark:border-yellow-700 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 mb-4">
      <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><strong>Esempio:</strong> Vuoi giocare nella nostra squadra?</p>
      <p class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 font-bold">Giocheresti nella nostra squadra? / Vorresti giocare nella nostra squadra?</p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-4">
      <div class="bg-yellow-50 dark:bg-yellow-900/30 border-2 border-yellow-200 dark:border-yellow-700 rounded-xl px-3 py-3">
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-2">• Vieni in pizzeria con me?</p>
        <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-yellow-500 dark:border-yellow-600 bg-transparent dark:text-white px-2 py-1 focus:outline-none focus:border-yellow-700 dark:focus:border-yellow-400 w-full" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="Verresti in pizzeria con me?|Vorresti venire in pizzeria con me?" placeholder="">
      </div>

      <div class="bg-yellow-50 dark:bg-yellow-900/30 border-2 border-yellow-200 dark:border-yellow-700 rounded-xl px-3 py-3">
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-2">• Mi aiuti a lavare l'automobile?</p>
        <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-yellow-500 dark:border-yellow-600 bg-transparent dark:text-white px-2 py-1 focus:outline-none focus:border-yellow-700 dark:focus:border-yellow-400 w-full" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="Mi aiuteresti a lavare l'automobile?|Vorresti aiutarmi a lavare l'automobile?" placeholder="">
      </div>

      <div class="bg-yellow-50 dark:bg-yellow-900/30 border-2 border-yellow-200 dark:border-yellow-700 rounded-xl px-3 py-3">
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-2">• Mi passi il sale?</p>
        <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-yellow-500 dark:border-yellow-600 bg-transparent dark:text-white px-2 py-1 focus:outline-none focus:border-yellow-700 dark:focus:border-yellow-400 w-full" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="Mi passeresti il sale?|Vorresti passarmi il sale?" placeholder="">
      </div>

      <div class="bg-yellow-50 dark:bg-yellow-900/30 border-2 border-yellow-200 dark:border-yellow-700 rounded-xl px-3 py-3">
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-2">• Mi presti per qualche giorno la tua macchina fotografica?</p>
        <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-yellow-500 dark:border-yellow-600 bg-transparent dark:text-white px-2 py-1 focus:outline-none focus:border-yellow-700 dark:focus:border-yellow-400 w-full" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="Mi presteresti per qualche giorno la tua macchina fotografica?|Vorresti prestarmi per qualche giorno la tua macchina fotografica?" placeholder="">
      </div>

      <div class="bg-yellow-50 dark:bg-yellow-900/30 border-2 border-yellow-200 dark:border-yellow-700 rounded-xl px-3 py-3">
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-2">• Mi accompagni a fare un giro in città?</p>
        <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-yellow-500 dark:border-yellow-600 bg-transparent dark:text-white px-2 py-1 focus:outline-none focus:border-yellow-700 dark:focus:border-yellow-400 w-full" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="Mi accompagneresti a fare un giro in città?|Vorresti accompagnarmi a fare un giro in città?" placeholder="">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Esercizio 2: Completa coniugando al congiuntivo imperfetto o trapassato -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl border-4 border-blue-200 dark:border-blue-700 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6" data-controller="fill-blanks">
    <h2 class="font-bold text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-400 mb-3">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
        <span class="bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">2</span>
        <span>Completa coniugando al <span class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 font-bold underline">congiuntivo imperfetto</span> o al <span class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 font-bold underline">congiuntivo trapassato</span> i verbi tra parentesi.</span>
      </div>
    </h2>

    <div class="bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/40 border-2 border-blue-200 dark:border-blue-700 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 mb-4">
      <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Se nella frase principale c'è un verbo al <strong>condizionale seguito da "che"</strong> nella frase che si collega alla prima c'è sempre il <strong>congiuntivo imperfetto</strong> o <strong>trapassato</strong>.</p>
      <p class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 font-bold mt-2">Vorrei che tu non dicessi bugie.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-3">
      <div class="bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/30 border-2 border-blue-200 dark:border-blue-700 rounded-xl px-3 py-3">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">• Vorrei che</span>
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-blue-500 dark:border-blue-600 bg-transparent dark:text-white px-2 py-1 focus:outline-none focus:border-blue-700 dark:focus:border-blue-400 w-48" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="mangiassi|tu mangiassi" placeholder="">
          <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">(mangiare).</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/30 border-2 border-blue-200 dark:border-blue-700 rounded-xl px-3 py-3">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">• Vorrei che</span>
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-blue-500 dark:border-blue-600 bg-transparent dark:text-white px-2 py-1 focus:outline-none focus:border-blue-700 dark:focus:border-blue-400 w-48" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="finissi|tu finissi" placeholder="">
          <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">(finire).</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/30 border-2 border-blue-200 dark:border-blue-700 rounded-xl px-3 py-3">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">• Vorrei che</span>
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-blue-500 dark:border-blue-600 bg-transparent dark:text-white px-2 py-1 focus:outline-none focus:border-blue-700 dark:focus:border-blue-400 w-48" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="raccontassi|tu raccontassi" placeholder="">
          <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">(raccontare).</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/30 border-2 border-blue-200 dark:border-blue-700 rounded-xl px-3 py-3">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">• Vorrei che</span>
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-blue-500 dark:border-blue-600 bg-transparent dark:text-white px-2 py-1 focus:outline-none focus:border-blue-700 dark:focus:border-blue-400 w-48" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="fossi|tu fossi" placeholder="">
          <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">(essere).</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/30 border-2 border-blue-200 dark:border-blue-700 rounded-xl px-3 py-3">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">• Vorrei che</span>
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-blue-500 dark:border-blue-600 bg-transparent dark:text-white px-2 py-1 focus:outline-none focus:border-blue-700 dark:focus:border-blue-400 w-48" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="avessi|tu avessi" placeholder="">
          <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">(avere).</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/30 border-2 border-blue-200 dark:border-blue-700 rounded-xl px-3 py-3">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">• Vorrei che</span>
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-blue-500 dark:border-blue-600 bg-transparent dark:text-white px-2 py-1 focus:outline-none focus:border-blue-700 dark:focus:border-blue-400 w-48" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="lavorassi|tu lavorassi" placeholder="">
          <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">(lavorare).</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Esercizio 3: Sottolinea le frasi con l'imperativo -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl border-4 border-green-200 dark:border-green-700 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6" data-controller="word-highlighter" data-word-highlighter-multi-color-value="false">
    <h2 class="font-bold text-green-700 dark:text-green-400 mb-3">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
        <span class="bg-green-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">3</span>
        <span>Sottolinea le frasi che esprimono un ordine con l'<span class="text-green-600 dark:text-green-400 font-bold underline">imperativo</span>.</span>
      </div>
    </h2>

    <!-- Hidden color selector -->
    <div class="hidden">
      <span data-word-highlighter-target="colorBox" data-color="green"></span>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-3 cursor-pointer">
      <div class="bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-900/30 border-2 border-green-200 dark:border-green-700 rounded-xl px-3 py-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">• <span data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="true" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" class="rounded">Chiudi la finestra!</span> / <span data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="false" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" class="rounded">Vorresti chiudere la finestra, per piacere?</span></span>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-900/30 border-2 border-green-200 dark:border-green-700 rounded-xl px-3 py-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">• <span data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="false" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" class="rounded">Vuoi prendere lo sciroppo?</span> / <span data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="true" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" class="rounded">Prendi lo sciroppo!</span></span>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-900/30 border-2 border-green-200 dark:border-green-700 rounded-xl px-3 py-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">• <span data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="true" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" class="rounded">Metti il cappotto!</span> / <span data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="false" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" class="rounded">Vuoi mettere il cappotto?</span></span>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-900/30 border-2 border-green-200 dark:border-green-700 rounded-xl px-3 py-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">• <span data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="false" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" class="rounded">Potreste fare un po' di silenzio?</span> / <span data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="true" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" class="rounded">State zitti!</span></span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="text-right text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6">
    Grammatica pp. <%= link_to "70", pagina_path("nvl5_gram_p070"), class: "text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 hover:text-red-800 dark:hover:text-red-300 underline font-bold" %>, <%= link_to "71", pagina_path("nvl5_gram_p071"), class: "text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 hover:text-red-800 dark:hover:text-red-300 underline font-bold" %>, <%= link_to "72", pagina_path("nvl5_gram_p072"), class: "text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 hover:text-red-800 dark:hover:text-red-300 underline font-bold" %>, <%= link_to "73", pagina_path("nvl5_gram_p073"), class: "text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 hover:text-red-800 dark:hover:text-red-300 underline font-bold" %>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise Controls -->
  <div class="mt-6">
    <%= render 'shared/exercise_controls' %>
  </div>
</div>
